This is a simple text adventure made using python.

Its very simple to use just follow the on screen instructions.

*Future tasks*

Add effects and cool-downs for the class powers
	
	- Rage next attack does x2 damage
	- Poison enemy's defence is weekend or takes extra damage 		  each turn
	- Fire ball a single high powered attack  

Add new enemy's, next goblin

Add items eg. Health Potion

Use level, and attack to work out damage. Then knock down for the defence.

Use endurance stat to work out the cool-downs  
